sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Platform Component
    participant Ingress as RHOAI Platform Ingress<br/>TLS Termination
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails<br/>Content Safety, Jailbreak,<br/>Topic Safety, SDD
    participant EmbedModels as Local NLP Models<br/>SpaCy, SentenceTransformers,<br/>FastEmbed (in-process)
    participant LLM as Upstream LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails<br/>Hallucination, Content Safety,<br/>Sensitive Data
    participant Redis as Redis (optional)<br/>6379/TCP
    participant OTEL as OpenTelemetry Collector

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    Ingress->>Server: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 (TLS terminated)<br/>Authorization header forwarded

    Server->>Server: Parse GuardrailsChatCompletionRequest<br/>Select config, resolve thread

    opt Thread Persistence Enabled
        Server->>Redis: Load thread state<br/>Redis protocol/6379<br/>Optional TLS
        Redis-->>Server: Thread history
    end

    Server->>InputRails: Execute input rails pipeline
    InputRails->>EmbedModels: Semantic similarity check<br/>(in-process, no network)
    EmbedModels-->>InputRails: Embedding vectors
    InputRails-->>Server: Input validation result<br/>(pass / blocked with reason)

    alt Input Rails Pass
        Server->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token / API Key
        LLM-->>Server: LLM Response

        Server->>OutputRails: Execute output rails pipeline
        OutputRails->>EmbedModels: Hallucination / safety check<br/>(in-process)
        EmbedModels-->>OutputRails: Embedding vectors
        OutputRails-->>Server: Output validation result<br/>(pass / modified / blocked)
    else Input Rails Block
        Server->>Server: Generate blocked response<br/>(no LLM call made)
    end

    opt Thread Persistence Enabled
        Server->>Redis: Save updated thread state<br/>Redis protocol/6379
    end

    Server->>OTEL: Export trace spans<br/>HTTP or gRPC<br/>Configurable endpoint
    Server-->>Ingress: JSON Response<br/>HTTP/8000
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 2: Standalone Guardrail Check

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token
    Ingress->>Server: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000

    Server->>InputRails: Execute rails on message
    InputRails->>EmbedModels: Evaluate message<br/>(in-process)
    EmbedModels-->>InputRails: Results

    opt Rail Requires LLM Evaluation
        InputRails->>LLM: LLM-based rail check<br/>HTTPS/443
        LLM-->>InputRails: LLM judgment
    end

    InputRails-->>Server: Validation result

    Server-->>Ingress: Check result (pass/fail + details)
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 3: OpenTelemetry Trace Export

    Server->>OTEL: Export spans<br/>HTTP/gRPC (configurable)<br/>OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT
